### What Rec1 is (policy — from live catalog terms)

- **Payment due at registration** — registration required before participation.
- **Online or in-person** at Susi Q Center.
- **Late registration** space-available only; fees **not pro-rated**; expire end of session.
- **Drop-ins:** City instructors may accept **checks only** (payable to "City of Laguna Beach"); registration form required; **no cash/credit** at drop-in.
- **Transfers:** Written request ≥1 business day before start; **$20 fee**.
- **Independent contractors** (LBTA coaches) represent the City on court.
- **Release of liability** must be on file.

