### Known friction (documented in SMS + bot KB)

1. **City catalog lags `/schedules` by 1–2 days** when sessions move or new classes publish.
2. **App/email confirmation ≠ enrolled** until **City card charges**.
3. **“Pay Later” in app** — credits loaded after City receipt (Week 2 email).
4. **Wrong class name** in catalog (e.g. “green dot” missing) — front desk holds manually.
5. **Multiple Rec1 deep links** in emails can go stale when City changes session IDs.

**Ops rule:** If it’s on `/schedules` but not Rec1 → don’t tell family to double-book; text **(949) 534-0457**.

