## Part 2 — User registration workflows (as built + as told)

### Workflow A — New family (recommended path)

```mermaid
flowchart LR
  A[Discover LBTA] --> B["/book — free trial"]
  B --> C[Coach placement + trial]
  C --> D["/schedules — pick program + frequency"]
  D --> E{Register modal}
  E -->|Path A| F[Rec1 — pay now]
  E -->|Path B| G[Lead form → /api/book]
  F --> H[City charge = spot held]
  G --> I[Staff calls → then Rec1]
  H --> J[Download LBTA app]
  I --> J
  J --> K[Check-in / weather / roster]
```

| Step | System | Owner |
|------|--------|-------|
| 1. Trial | `lagunabeachtennisacademy.com/book` | LBTA |
| 2. Choose program | `/schedules` (SSOT) | LBTA data |
| 3. Pay | **Rec1** (or in-person City) | **City** |
| 4. Operate | **LBTA app** (iOS/Android) | LBTA / PlayByPoint |
| 5. Questions | support@ / (949) 534-0457 | Saska / desk |

### Workflow B — Returning player (knows program)

```mermaid
flowchart LR
  A["/schedules"] --> B[Register]
  B --> C[Path A: Rec1 tab]
  C --> D[Pay at City]
  D --> E[App for schedule]
```

